{"tid":874363,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【港台電視31】獅子山下2018：定風波 (銅鑼灣書店,林榮基書店)","createTime":"2018-10-24T06:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T07:38:27.000Z","uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35b7413142bdec61ffb728aa9a372d9542abff36","tid":874363,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FPXji0LP3ys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFPXji0LP3ys&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAFxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a32339ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FPXji0LP3ys</a><br />\n<br />\n故事改編自銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基剛從內地回港後的經歷。林榮基按指示回港取書店的電腦把讀者資料帶回深圳，林被安排到油麻地的酒店暫住，只能在香港逗留兩天。回港後，他發現同事給他的不是正確的電腦，從而他開始想像除了服從內地部門的其他可能。他走在油麻地的街頭，觀察到香港人各式其色的生活姿態，重新感受到香港人擁有的自由氣氛。離開前，他在九龍塘地鐵站外躊躇，靜靜地下了留港的決定。<br />\n<br />\n編導：陳上城<br />\n主演：阮志雄（雄仔叔叔）"},{"pid":"48874878c83eb3e69c50bbc3bb994f4347ec7212","tid":874363,"uid":82078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇咗 依家個情況比當時更差<br />\n地鐵啲人都係冇理會個新聞"},{"pid":"f4752a6611584d24980789261db65110e9f64f87","tid":874363,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0b07f7ccf9c61cda0d64c9155918272da81922e9","tid":874363,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}